OL,6,FA year-long investigation by ITV News
OL,7,Fhas exposed the scale of the harm
OL,8,Fcaused by a drug given to pregnant
OL,9,Fwomen for decades, Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent and Senior Producer
OL,11,FLottie Kilraine report
OL,13,FThe chair of the Health Select
OL,14,FCommittee is writing an urgent letter
OL,15,Fto Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,16,Fcriticising the government's lack of
OL,17,Faction over the "absolutely
OL,18,Foutrageous" DES pregnancy drug
OL,19,Fscandal, after a year-long ITV News
OL,20,Finvestigation.
