OL,3,CPressure grows on government to act on
OL,4,CDES pregnancy drug scandal
OL,6,FStilbestrol, commonly known as DES,
OL,7,Fwas a synthetic hormone prescribed to
OL,8,Fan estimated 300,000 women on the NHS
OL,9,Fbetween the late 1930s and 1980s to
OL,10,Ftreat several issues, including
OL,11,Fmiscarriage, until it was linked to
OL,12,Frare cancers and infertility in the
OL,13,Fdaughters of those who took it.
OL,15,FLayla Moran MP, who chairs the
OL,16,Fcommittee responsible for scrutinising
OL,17,Fthe Department of Health, said there
OL,18,Fis a "lack of urgency" from government
OL,19,Fin addressing the harms caused by the
OL,20,Fdrug, which was prescribed to pregnant
OL,21,Fwomen on the NHS for decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
