OL,6,FIt follows calls from campaigners for
OL,7,Fa statutory public inquiry, after our
OL,8,Freporting exposed the failures of the
OL,9,Fhealth authorities to act on safety
OL,10,Fwarnings about the drug's sinister
OL,11,Fside effects.
OL,13,FLayla Moran MP, chair of the Health
OL,14,FSelect Committee, says she is writing
OL,15,Fan urgent letter to the Health
OL,16,FSecretary Wes Streeting following a
OL,17,Fyear-long ITV News investigation into
OL,18,Fthe drug DES
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
