OL,6,F"It's absolutely outrageous that this
OL,7,Fhappened and I think quite
OL,8,Funderstandably people want answers,"
OL,9,FMoran told ITV News.
OL,11,F"I'm really shocked at both the number
OL,12,Fof people affected but also the lack
OL,13,Fof urgency that seems to be coming
OL,14,Ffrom the government's department over
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
