OL,6,F"After this many decades of these
OL,7,Ffamilies being failed by the state, we
OL,8,Fshould be reaching a rapid conclusion
OL,9,Fto this as quickly as possible,
OL,10,Fbecause if we act now it will save
OL,11,Flives."
OL,13,FMoran is demanding the government
OL,14,Ftakes steps to trace and inform the
OL,15,Festimated hundreds of thousands of
OL,16,Fwomen exposed to the drug and find out
OL,17,Fwhy families concerns have been
OL,18,Fignored for so long.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
