OL,6,F"We know that female voices in
OL,7,Fhealthcare systems are very often
OL,8,Fignored, this is a well trodden path,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"Medical misogyny is real, we know it
OL,12,Fhappens and they've admitted it
OL,13,Fhappens, so the question now is what
OL,14,Fdo we do about it. The Department for
OL,15,FHealth have said they are
OL,16,Finvestigating, well give us a
OL,17,Ftimescale.
