OL,6,FShe said women have disproportionately
OL,7,Fbeen at the core of high profile
OL,8,Fmedical scandals, including vaginal
OL,9,Fmesh, sodium valporate and primodos.
OL,11,F"DES in particular was used decades
OL,12,Fago but its very misleading to refer
OL,13,Fto it as a legacy or historical
OL,14,Fscandal because the impacts are still
OL,15,Fbeing felt by women today, and they
OL,16,Furgently need help," Dr Macloed told
OL,17,FITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
