OL,6,F"These women need the care. They need
OL,7,Fthe screening, they need the correct
OL,8,Fmedical treatment and they need the
OL,9,Fawareness among medical professionals
OL,10,Fof what DES is and what the impacts
OL,11,Fare because a lot of the younger
OL,12,Fgeneration of doctors simply will not
OL,13,Fbe aware of this and what it does."
