OL,6,FMs Toale told ITV News she believes
OL,7,FDES is "potentially one of the biggest
OL,8,Fpharmaceutical scandals we will ever
OL,9,Fhave seen in British history".
OL,11,FJan, 75, from Bournemouth West,
OL,12,Fbelieves her mother Rita was
OL,13,Fprescribed the drug during three
OL,14,Fpregnancies and that exposure
OL,15,Fcontributed to her death, aged 32,
OL,16,Ffrom breast cancer in 1951, when Jan
OL,17,Fwas a toddler.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
