OL,6,FLabour MP Jesssica Toale says she
OL,7,Fbelieves the scale of the pregnancy
OL,8,Fdrug DES, exposed by a year-long ITV
OL,9,FNews investigation, is 'potentially
OL,10,Fone of the biggest pharmaceutical
OL,11,Fscandals in British history'
OL,13,F"There are of course a range of views
OL,14,Fof what they want to see, some want an
OL,15,Fapology, some want compensation for
OL,16,Fthe struggles and trials they have
OL,17,Fbeen through," Ms Toale told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
