OL,6,F"I think first and foremost the
OL,7,Fmessage that came out so clearly to me
OL,8,Fwas that they want acknowledgement and
OL,9,Fawareness amongst the NHS. There's not
OL,10,Feven a web page on the NHS website
OL,11,Fthat explains what DES is."
OL,13,FAlongside a public inquiry,
OL,14,Fcampaigners are calling for an
OL,15,Finformation campaign to ensure
OL,16,Fhealthcare professionals are aware of
OL,17,FDES, medical research into the long-
OL,18,Fterm, intergenerational effects of the
OL,19,Fdrug, targeted screening for cancers
OL,20,Fand fertility issues and a
OL,21,Fcompensation fund.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
