OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "There are
OL,8,Fharrowing accounts of harm caused by
OL,9,Fthe historic use of
OL,10,FDiethylstilboestrol (DES), with some
OL,11,Fwomen still suffering from the
OL,12,Fassociated risks of this medication
OL,13,Fwhich have been passed down a
OL,14,Fgeneration, and not feeling adequately
OL,15,Flistened to or supported.
