OL,6,F"The Secretary of State has been clear
OL,7,Fhe has been looking seriously at this
OL,8,Flegacy issue and carefully considering
OL,9,Fwhat more the government can do to
OL,10,Fbetter support women and their
OL,11,Ffamilies who have been impacted.
OL,13,F"As a result, he has asked NHS England
OL,14,Fto urgently work closely with local
OL,15,Fcancer alliances to make sure that GPs
OL,16,Fare aware of the follow up guidance
OL,17,Ffor those exposed to DES, so that
OL,18,Fthose who could benefit from
OL,19,Fadditional screening aren't missing
OL,20,Fout."
